put these libraries in lib/:

markdown2.py    # markdown2 lib
pymongo/        # python-client for mongodb
mongokit/       # wrapper for pymongo
tornado/        # tornado web server + framework
web/            # web.py framework. i use it form component.
beaker/         # beaker caching lib
scrappy/        # ls

also, install mongodb (statically compiled ver available) 
and python-simplejson.

